remixlab.bias

Class EventGrabberTuple

  • java.lang.Object
    • remixlab.bias.EventGrabberTuple

  • public class EventGrabberTuple
extends Object
    A [BogusEvent,Grabber] tuple. An enqueued tuple fires Grabber.performInteraction(BogusEvent) call from the event in the tuple.

    Tuples are typically enqueued by an agent (see Agent.handle(BogusEvent)), but may be enqueued manually, see InputHandler.enqueueEventTuple(EventGrabberTuple).
